  "texts": [
    "By itself, ResNet-50 contributed a test accuracy of 89.2% with an IoU of 0.88, while the use of DWT in concert with SVM further refine and classify features with increased efficacy.",
    "By itself, U-Net had a Dice Coefficient of 0.91, and for this challenge, this was substantially enhanced with the hybrid approach in PolynetDWTCADx.",
    "Compared to more complex architectures, such as Vision Transformers, PolynetDWTCADx manages a good trade-off between computational efficiency and interpretability.",
    "These models usually require large amounts of training data and computational resources.",
    "The proposed framework uses pretrained CNNs with DWT combined for competitive results on the medium-sized dataset CKHK-22."
